{"tid":2494832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國手遊自創「精靈語」！台灣網友一看傻眼：就是注音符號","createTime":"2021-04-18T22:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T23:43:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e7670d8874c379a9b201beea94dc93b52fbe9644","tid":2494832,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:23:37.000Z","msg":"中國手遊自創「精靈語」！台灣網友一看傻眼：就是注音符號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3500009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3500009&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVphjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=38dfec05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3500009&h=1554f172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3500009</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國網易公司今年開發的手遊《天諭》中，自創了一種新種族，並使用「精靈語」溝通，讓玩家花費時間爭相解讀該語言文字，但台灣網友一看，赫然發現根本就是台灣人從小學習的注音符號，傻眼直呼「根本就剽竊」、「原來我們有精靈血統」；還有人笑稱：「完了 我們的密語被對岸破解了」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，在遊戲《天諭》中，玩家會得到一封由該遊戲自創的種族「汐族」族人間往來、使用特殊「精靈語」文字來溝通的信件，雖然不懂信件內容也能完成遊戲任務，但一位對此相當有興趣玩家卻花了3個小時將內容解出，最後將翻譯結果PO網，並公布羅馬拼音與此「精靈語」的對照表，引發討論。<br />\n<br />\n但台灣網友一看該信件，才發現所謂「精靈語」，就是台灣人從小學習的注音符號「ㄅㄆㄇㄈ」，網友將相關新聞轉PO在PTT上，並表示「X，不就注音文？」他並諷刺，第一次看到別人賣力解讀注音，而且還不知道那是注音，「讓我從奇怪的地方獲得了奇怪的優越感」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">對此，其他鄉民也紛紛留言「原來我是精靈族」、「中國研究：台灣人有精靈血統」、「送他們小學國語課本當攻略」、「完了 我們的密碼要被破解了」、「網易用注音當獨立種族的語言是不是暗示支持台灣人的種族獨立性」、「搞分裂 舉報台獨了」、「這樣我們就沒有共匪檢測器能用了」。<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b3729fbaef0e708887ef9d79e3375c5d186c31b6","tid":2494832,"uid":258784,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:35:32.000Z","msg":"幫樓豬補返張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4eda8883350436ee742fdee5d60fae38cf2e66","tid":2494832,"uid":100680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:52:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2493843/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2493843/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n等陣裏面d五毛又走入黎話抄襲係啱，台灣有咩資格嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6863438bfbdfd1a2a7e1ce79ddfe9a0695f77c","tid":2494832,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:57:15.000Z","msg":"好好wor<br />\n可以用黎推廣台語<br />\n由以前感覺老土變做精靈語咁有靈氣"},{"pid":"d93f12d591da654901ce87a07fb3374099cfce9b","tid":2494832,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:58:27.000Z","msg":"大陸冇原創"},{"pid":"e3bccd80e596981dd16be9d767ba48831624ee75","tid":2494832,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前打得機多，台仔成日用<br />\n打到有啲注音符號而家都識睇"},{"pid":"4f0e59e90e51415c9d0d144313b5f89f748a1cd8","tid":2494832,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93f12d591da654901ce87a07fb3374099cfce9b","tid":2494832,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:58:27.000Z","msg":"大陸冇原創"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:00:15.000Z","msg":"Hk no IT"},{"pid":"da71ad706e123d8f30c8d34055c309bb36f0c435","tid":2494832,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d93f12d591da654901ce87a07fb3374099cfce9b","tid":2494832,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T22:58:27.000Z","msg":"大陸冇原創"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:02:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2493843/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2493843/page/1</a><br />\n無原創都算<br />\n入面成堆五毛仲話中國抄都抄得咁成功，叫香港台灣日本人好好反省下點解做唔到中國人咁成功"},{"pid":"b5ab236af9948f96e1461d3b5423